description: In this listing you are buying 3 Grams of this High Quality ORGANIC DMT Crystals (in some cases powder)! (no chemicals used from growing the bush, to the crystals, all process is toxic chemical free)We have mastered the way of extracting DMT so we dont have to use any toxic chemicals which makes everything easy, and yield to be significant bigger, we enjoy taking it slow. Our process takes about a week or so, as to compare to chemical way which lets you get DMT out of the plant in 1-2 days.I recommend the following doses when smoking my NN-DMT:Beginners 20-30mgExperienced 50mgSpace Cadets 60mgNN-DMT should be smoked in a vaporiser or a pipe/bong. When smoking with a pipe/bong it is strongly advised to place a layer of cigarette ash onto the gauze before placing the NN-DMT onto the layer of ash. Please note that my batches of NN-DMT vary in colour, ranging from beige to a light shade of brown. This is due to the variables in batches of Mimosa Hostilis bark in addition to the many variables associated with the extraction process. The shade of the final product never influences the potency of the NN-DMT batch.ã-WIKIã-N,N-Dimethyltryptamine (DMT or N,N-DMT) is a tryptamine molecule which occurs in many plants and animals.[3] It can be consumed as a powerful psychedelic drug and has historically been prepared by various cultures for ritual purposes.[4] Rick Strassman labeled it –the spirit molecule”.[5] In most countries, DMT is illegal. DMT has a relatively short duration of action, intense effects and rapid onset. For that reason, DMT was known as the –businessmanês trip” during the 1960s in the United States, as a user could access the full depth of a psychedelic experience in considerably less time than with other substances such as LSD or magic mushrooms.[6] DMT can be inhaled, injected, vaped or orally ingested, and its effects depend on the dose. When inhaled or injected, the effects last a short period of time: about 5 to 15 minutes. Effects can last 3 hours or more when orally ingested along with an MAOI, such as the ayahuasca brew of many native Amazonian tribes.[7] DMT can produce vivid –projections” of mystical experiences involving euphoria and dynamic hallucinations of geometric forms.[8] It is a structural analog of serotonin and melatonin and a functional analog of other psychedelic tryptamines such as 4-AcO-DMT, 5-MeO-DMT, 5-HO-DMT, psilocybin (4-PO-DMT), and psilocin (4-HO-DMT)._IMPORTANT SHIPPING INFORMATIONãBefore I begin, I want to let you know super important piece of requirements: Please write your real name and your real address in format: JOHN SMITH 123 MAIN STREET CITY, STATE ZIPCODE    PLEASE FINALIZE UPON DELIVERY, IF YOU WAIT FOR YOUR ORDER TO AUTO-FINALIZE YOU WILL BE BLACKLISTED/BANNED ORDERING FROM US!!!    ALL ORDERS WILL BE SHIPPED WITHIN 24-48 HOURS AFTER BEING MARKED ACCEPTED !!! SO PLEASE BE PATIENT AND STOP ASKING WHERE IS YOUR PACKAGE 2-3 DAYS AFTER YOUR ORDER HAS BEEN MARKED SHIPPED, PRIORITY MAIL USUALLY TAKES 2-4 DAYS IN SOME CASES LONGER DEPEND ON HOW BUSY MAIL POSTS ARE, SO PLACE YOUR ORDERS ACCORDINGLY AND ALLOW AROUND 5-7 DAYS FROM PLACING AN ORDER TO RECEIVING IT.    DO NOT ASK FOR TRACKING NUMBERS - They will only be given for verification purposes in orders where an issue may have arisen.    If your package shows as any of the tracking updates below - NO REFUNDS -NO RESHIPS: -Delivered -Left and door/mailbox/porch/to person etc. -Not deliverable as addressed -Return to Sender -RejectedAny shipping issues or mistakes on our side we will automatically reship. Anything else just ask and we will figure out a solution! Thank You and have a Good Day!

Volles Spektrum bedeutet, dass neben dem Cannabinoid THC noch weitere Cannabidoide in hoher Konzentration enthalten sind, wie z.B. CBD, CBDa und THCa. Jedes Cannabinoid hat seine Eigenschaften und Einsatzgebiet. Neben einem angenehmen High hat das ƒl also einen hohen medizinischen Nutzen.Wax, auch bekannt als Dab, Crumble, Sugar, Honeycomb und Budder wird unter der Verwendung von Butan (ein Flôssiggas) als L_sungsmittel fôr die Extraktion der wichtigsten Cannabinoide und Terpene aus den Cannabisblôten hergestellt. Das daraus entstehende Gemisch wird dann zu einem Konzentrat verarbeitet, das ein bisschen wie Bienenwachs aussieht. Der Herstellungsprozess von Cannabis-Wax variiert und kann in einer Vielzahl verschiedener Produkte mit einzigartigen Beschaffenheiten und Farben resultieren. Per Vakuum werden die letzten Reste von Butangas entfernt, ein absolutes HQ Produkt.Es gibt verschiedene Methoden, Cannabisextrakte wie Wax zu konsumieren. Bedenke, dass manche besonders flôssigen, klebrigen oder sonst wie hart zu handhabenden Wachse sich nicht sonderlich eignen, in einen Joint gemischt oder in einem Verdampfer oder einer Haschpfeife verwendet zu werden und sie k_nnen den Einsatz einer Dab- oder Oil-Rig erforderlich machen.Allerdings kann man das Konzentrat in den Kôhlschrank legen, so erh_rtet es und man kann es besser handhaben. Gern br_sel ich mir so etwas oben in den Joint.Haschpfeifen:Es gibt einige neuere Haschpfeifen auf dem Markt, die es Konsumenten erm_glichen, ohne Probleme Konzentrate wie Wachse zu genie_en. Auf diese Art musst Du nicht in einen anspruchsvolleren (teureren) Verdampfer oder eine Rig investieren. Achte darauf, dass die von Dir gekaufte Pfeife speziell fôr l_semittelbasierte Extrakte und nicht nur fôr Kief oder normales Hasch geeignet ist.Verdampfer:Verdampfer sind die beste Option fôr alle, die den gesundheitsgef_hrdenden Risiken des Rauchens aus dem Weg gehen wollen. Obwohl Verdampfer traditionell nicht fôr Extrakte ausgelegt sind, k_nnen manche neuere Modelle dafôr verwendet werden.Allerdings sind die meisten dieser Modelle tragbar und minderwertigeren Verdampfern wird nachgesagt, schlecht zu ziehen. Wahrscheinlich weil sie die hohen Temperaturen nicht erreichen k_nnen, die fôr das ordentliche Verdampfen von Konzentraten notwendig sind.Dabbing:Extrakte wie Wax werden oft als –Dabs” bezeichnet, da Dabbing die h_ufigste Art des Konsums ist. Dabbing umfasst die Verwendung spezieller Werkzeuge: Einem –Nagel”, einem Bunsenbrenner und einer Dab-Rig.Der Nagel wird ôblicherweise mit dem Bunsenbrenner erhitzt (oder elektronisch, wenn Du einen E-Nail hast) und eine kleine Menge des Konzentrats wird auf der Spitze platziert. Der von der Hitze entwickelte Dampf wird dann mit einer speziellen Pfeife inhaliert, die oft Wasser als Filter verwendet.Vapepen:Ich kann den Puffco+V2 w_rmstens empfehlen, er hat eine Kammer fôr das BHO und alternativ auch ein Schraubgewinde, um Cartridges oder andere Eliquids zu konsumieren. Ein echter Hingucker und ein tolles Raucherlebnis.

Neben einem angenehmen High hat das ƒl also einen hohen medizinischen Nutzen.Wax, auch bekannt als Dab, Crumble, Sugar, Honeycomb und Budder wird unter der Verwendung von Butan (ein Flôssiggas) als L_sungsmittel fôr die Extraktion der wichtigsten Cannabinoide und Terpene aus den Cannabisblôten hergestellt. Das daraus entstehende Gemisch wird dann zu einem Konzentrat verarbeitet, das ein bisschen wie Bienenwachs aussieht. Der Herstellungsprozess von Cannabis-Wax variiert und kann in einer Vielzahl verschiedener Produkte mit einzigartigen Beschaffenheiten und Farben resultieren. Per Vakuum werden die letzten Reste von Butangas entfernt, ein absolutes HQ Produkt.Es gibt verschiedene Methoden, Cannabisextrakte wie Wax zu konsumieren. Bedenke, dass manche besonders flôssigen, klebrigen oder sonst wie hart zu handhabenden Wachse sich nicht sonderlich eignen, in einen Joint gemischt oder in einem Verdampfer oder einer Haschpfeife verwendet zu werden und sie k_nnen den Einsatz einer Dab- oder Oil-Rig erforderlich machen.Allerdings kann man das Konzentrat in den Kôhlschrank legen, so erh_rtet es und man kann es besser handhaben. Gern br_sel ich mir so etwas oben in den Joint.Haschpfeifen:Es gibt einige neuere Haschpfeifen auf dem Markt, die es Konsumenten erm_glichen, ohne Probleme Konzentrate wie Wachse zu genie_en. Auf diese Art musst Du nicht in einen anspruchsvolleren (teureren) Verdampfer oder eine Rig investieren. Achte darauf, dass die von Dir gekaufte Pfeife speziell fôr l_semittelbasierte Extrakte und nicht nur fôr Kief oder normales Hasch geeignet ist.Verdampfer:Verdampfer sind die beste Option fôr alle, die den gesundheitsgef_hrdenden Risiken des Rauchens aus dem Weg gehen wollen. Obwohl Verdampfer traditionell nicht fôr Extrakte ausgelegt sind, k_nnen manche neuere Modelle dafôr verwendet werden.Allerdings sind die meisten dieser Modelle tragbar und minderwertigeren Verdampfern wird nachgesagt, schlecht zu ziehen. Wahrscheinlich weil sie die hohen Temperaturen nicht erreichen k_nnen, die fôr das ordentliche Verdampfen von Konzentraten notwendig sind.Dabbing:Extrakte wie Wax werden oft als –Dabs” bezeichnet, da Dabbing die h_ufigste Art des Konsums ist. Dabbing umfasst die Verwendung spezieller Werkzeuge: Einem –Nagel”, einem Bunsenbrenner und einer Dab-Rig.Der Nagel wird ôblicherweise mit dem Bunsenbrenner erhitzt (oder elektronisch, wenn Du einen E-Nail hast) und eine kleine Menge des Konzentrats wird auf der Spitze platziert. Der von der Hitze entwickelte Dampf wird dann mit einer speziellen Pfeife inhaliert, die oft Wasser als Filter verwendet.Vapepen:Ich kann den Puffco+V2 w_rmstens empfehlen, er hat eine Kammer fôr das BHO und alternativ auch ein Schraubgewinde, um Cartridges oder andere Eliquids zu konsumieren. Ein echter Hingucker und ein tolles Raucherlebnis.

listing: Flubromazolam Solution 10mL @ 1mg/mL
description: This is not for vaping, although some say it is theoretically possible, it would be hugely wasteful. This is a proper solution intended to go directly into the mouth (hold under the tongue for awhile for fuller experience) and then followed with whatever culinary research method you prefer. The bioavailability of this method is in the high 90s percent making all other methods unnessary and wasteful at best but possibly dangerous considering the unkowns of bypassing the metabolic pathways it was designed for.IntroThis is a listing for a 10mL Flubromazolam PG solution mixed at 1mg/mL. Flubromazolam is the strongest of the several fluorinated benzo analogues, with an equipotency to 1mg of alprazolam (xanax) being roughly 0.25:1. That means taking only 0.25mg of flubromazolam is as strong as a 1mg does of alprazolam, or 1mg of flubromazolam would be like taking 4mg of alprazolam. This along with clonazolam - which has a similar equipotency - are some of the strongest RC benzos available and need to be handled carefully.Optional Paragraph    That is why accurate dosing is so important. The best method for this is still volumetric dosing. This method when done properly allows the product to be evenly distributed in a solution which is then dosed by volume, based on the ratio of mass to volume. Itês hard to mess up volumetric dosing but it can be done if itês not understood why it works. Measuring smaller amounts yields higher error ranges and vice versa. Having a scale with a large acceptable error tolerance could also be problematic. Basically if youêre vendor canêt tell you what the error range per standard dose of their solution or canêt explain how they derived it, then they are winging it and potentially putting people at risk. Especially if dealing with substances that are pschoactive at the microgram level like flubromazolam. Our error range for any solution will never be greater than +/- 5% of the standard dose. And that will be improving. If you have questions about this please PM us and weêll be happy to talk with you about it.CharacteristicsA distinguishing factor about FLam is its extremely long half life, having a duration of up to 18 hours. Thatês one of the longest durations in the benzo family, giving it a subjectively different experience than that of etizolam, alprazolam, or clonazolam whose durations are shorter but more intense. It is said to be more sedative and hypnotic in effect rather than euphoric and disinhibiting which some of the others produce. The long half life does provide for a smoother landing however, with the caveat of longer amnesia if used irresposibly, which is highly undesirable. Accurate dosing is the absolute solution to to these potential pitfalls.LogisticsThese are going to be shipped in high quality, stealthed leak-proof bottles. It will come with a 1mL sealed syringe (no needle) with 100-unit gradations per mL syringe for highly accurate dosing. You can either squeeze the nozzle into the syringe mouth and pull back, or take the nozzle off completely and draw from the bottle. Either way the bottle stays leak proof. The labels are a little confusing but donêt worry there is nothing in it aside from the active ingredient and the solvent at a ratio of 1mg/mL.With an equipotency ratio to alprozolam of 0.25:1 and solution of 1mg/mL, taking 0.25mL (25 units) of solution is equal to 1 mg alp (a football), 0.5mL gets you to 2mg alp (a bar), and the whole 1ml syringe would be equivalent to two bars.Cautions and Further ReadingDo not try to vape or inject (do not IV) this solution - it is meant to be ingested how Lil Wayne takes lean or Birdman: in mouth or possibly plugged, but I am unfamiliar with the second option and got nothin but respek for Birdman so I suggest the oral route, holding it under the tongue for half a minute for faster sublingual absorbtion if so desired.As always heed the warnings in the provided link, but especially so with flubromazolam and the other super strong benzo RCs, as their strength can be decieving. Your ability to assess your own intoxication becomes ineffective. Flam is an outstanding benzo but if youêre new to the scene or a habitual user of one of the other depressents listed at the top of the link below, I would highly advise you to start with something below the potency of alprazolam first.https://psychonautwiki.org/wiki/Flubromazolam

Where these methods differ from other extraction processes is in the amount of time harvested cannabis plants are allowed to dry and cure before the extraction.This Indica-dominant extract is made from fresh, uncured plants in order to preserve the delicate terpene (flavor) profile. Live resin is produced through a solvent-based extraction process that uses butane to extract the sought-after components. The resulting product has an ideal consistency for medical use.When you inhale a dab of this live resin, it feels like a breath of fresh air and is known to be very smooth! Plus, with THC content of 95-98% pure, you can bet that the –high” is borderline unparalleled. Best dabbed out of an oil rig or vape pen, it can also be dabbed in a joint or bong.Patients who have developed a preference for cannabis extracts or concentrates, such as shatter, butter and wax, will find live resin to be an ideal fit. The extraction process and high-end flower yield a full-flavored terpene profile nearly unmatched by most other extracts. You will taste the difference.

listing: 30ml Blazing Vapor THC Cannabis Vape eJuice
description: Blazing Vapor is a potent THC eJuice blend containing Purple OG Kush and Phantom Cookies and can be vaped as is for a super strong and intense high, or diluted with Vegetable Glycol (VG) and/or Propylene Glycol (PG) to make your oil last longer.FLAVORMany of you have told us you prefer the natural taste of pot so we havenêt added any flavors but feel free to add your own. Adding flavor masks that give away smell of pot and allows you to vape undetected in public. Now thatês a bonus!INFUSED NOT EXTRACTEDBlazing Vapor is infused with a 67% VG to 33% PG ratio. No butane or propane (lighter fuel), ethanol (alcohol) or isopropyl (rubbing alcohol) has been used in the cannabis extraction process.CONCENTRATEWhen used undiluted it can clog your vaporizerês coil faster than a nicotine infusion. While both PG and VG will work to extend the life of your coil, PG is thinner and will keep your coil unclogged the longest.For those unfamiliar with VG and PG, these two products are found in just about all eliquids and in the case of Blazing Vapor work to suspend cannabis trichomes until heat is applied which converts THC to its psychedelic form which is what gets you high. VG produces the billowing clouds of vapor often associated with vaping and has a sweeter taste, while PG produced much less smoke and has a throat hit that is often preferred by smokers. Many users prefer to dilute with a combination of both PG and VG.VAPORIZER SETTINGSWe recommend you set your vaporizer to around 50W for the optimal vaping experience. If youêre not feeling an effect experiment with different temperature settings.BOTTLINGThis listing is for 30ml Blazing Vapor which will be shipped in a 30ml vial. If you would prefer to receive your order as separate 10ml vials then include a message when supplying a shipping address.STEALTHWe use various methods to avoid detection and your Blazing Vapor will be unlabeled. The images are for illustrative purpose.ORDERING ESCROWKindly finalize your order to release the funds when they are held in escrow.

listing: Wookie #7 x Space Monkey (Gorilla Glue 4 x Wookie #15)
description: As always:Grown by meIndoor with renewable energy. Indoor quality with an outdoor carbon foot print.Organically grown in soil for extra terpene expression and quality.Hand manicured while –wet” to keep as many crystals on the bud as possible.Cured to perfection!This should be priced like my tier 1, but Iêm going to list this as tier 2 which is 10% cheaper due to the LIGHTLY SEEDED status. Also having a 20% sale so please take advantage of it while it lasts!!LIGHTLY SEEDED TLDR;(too long didnêt read): This new crop has some seeds unfortunately. Iêve removed the heavily seeded buds to be used for Live Rosin, and removed all the seeds that I saw when trimming, but there are still a small amount of seeds you may come across. This doesnêt matter much to vapers, but for you dirty smoking combusters out thereÄ Youêve been warned. They are easy enough to avoid in the grinder. This is still fantastic herb, but I have to be upfront and honest and warn you. Iêve sent out some samples to some of my regular customers and no one seemed to mind an occasional seed here or there.You might even want to keep what you find incase you want to try and grow some in the future. Alternatively throw them into government gardens as a form of protest.If you are still interested please read on.PEDIGREEWookie #7 x Space Monkey (Gorilla Glue 4 x Wookie #15)Orgasmatron and Wookie are known as Bodhiês best concentrate strains. They are smell and flavour sensations to say the least.https://en.seedfinder.eu/strain-info/Wookie/Bodhi_Seeds/This Wookie (Big Buddyês Lavender x Appalachia), a personal selection from Bodhi Seeds, has the most addictive aroma we have ever come across in the cannabis world. She smells like you just ripped your hand down a lavender vine and added a nose tingling sour note to it. The aroma is downright irresistible, the concentrate is potent as ever. Its something you would want your house, car, and office to smell like.The stankiest beast in our garden, she is one sour flower, a nose burner to the highest level, and a true powerhouse.https://en.seedfinder.eu/strain-info/Space_Monkey/Bodhi_Seeds/Space Monkey is a cross between the Gorilla Glue 4 x Wookie 15 blasting it into the far reaches of marijuana possibilities. The Wookie genetics add more resin and space fuel together with lavender, grape and fuel notes to both scent and taste. The effect is well-balanced yet deeply powerful. Flowering takes a total of 9 weeks to harvest.Due to this cross' extreme poly-hydrid nature, theres definitely some variation between the individuals. All are entrancingly terpy in the smell department and really nice buds. Cerebral, yet relaxing.Feel free to tell me with your address if you would like a specific one, or if you ask nicely Iêll let you pick 2.W2: Sour, spice, sweet, earthy, floral, Absinthe, with a hint of sexy dancing sweaty hippie girl.W5: Large slightly spongy buds Smell: Sour, Fuel, Citrus zest, grape, strawberry, mint, floral. Taste: Just like it smells. Sunset Sherbet cocktail with a mint garnish.W8: I mixed a lot of this into the Ground 0 mix, but its unique so I left some out. It reminds me of the strain Sherbet. Sweet, sour, orange, lime, cherry earth, mint.W9: Sweet Sour lemon lime, fuel, earth, floralGround 0 mix (W3,4, some of 8) 10% extra free(remind me if you pick this please). Ground 0 and the 2 closest plants. Statistically they may have more seeds than the others, but all heavily seeded buds were used to make live rosin. Its quite magical fishing through a bag of this due to the variation of the different sisters.Smells: sweet, watermelon, sour lemon-lime, fuel, mint, floral, earth.Sorry it took me an extra 2 months to get these listed, but on the bright side the herb got an extra 2 month cure. Thats always a good thing :DReason for the delay is Iêve been crazy busy with my total grow room rehaul and upgrades. Iêve taken 2 giant leaps. 1 from HPS grow lights to cutting edge state of the art leds. Iêve also moved from bottled organics to notill organic living soil. I only use plain water now and organic dry amendments are added to the soil that even has worms living in it. The whole focus now is on the soil food web. Prepare for some extreme terpene expressions on my future crops.If you like this, your going to love the Live Rosin Iêm making from this as well.If you followed me on CGMC you probably saw me announce this exciting seed test that I just finished.The seed test was for 2 currently unreleased crosses from Bodhi Seeds. Bodhi is one of the most sought after Breeders on the Planet. All while being family owned and operated. Bodhi himself, produces unique, high-quality cannabis crosses. Utilizing organic and sustainable practices, Bodhi creates some of the highest quality genetics and effective flowers available today. Hes done some podcasts, check him out if thats something you are into. I suggest the 2 parter on The POTCAST with Heavy Daze.I have a big place in my heart for Bodhi. The work he does, him as a lovely person in general, and his attitude towards breeding checks all the boxes for me. As soon as I heard him say that he loves to help plants have sex, I knew I found some one that vibes with me. That and all of his practices jive with my own.If youêve had the opportunity to try either Black Raspberry(currently sold out, OMG its so magic, and just so happens to be half Wookie) or Sunshine Daydream, youêll have a good idea on what some of his genetics can do.I was lucky enough to use an old contact on the west coast to request an opportunity to seed test for the man himself. I was graciously received 1 pack each of:Wookie 7(Black Raspberryês uncle) x Space Monkey (Gorilla Glue 4 x Wookie #15) https://en.seedfinder.eu/strain-info/Space_Monkey/Bodhi_Seeds/Orgasmatron x •88G13HP https://en.seedfinder.eu/strain-info/Wookie_Orgasm/Bodhi_Seeds/The cool thing about a seed test is that weêre both doing each other a favour. Iêm helping him test unreleased seeds to make sure there are no problems and give him a detailed report back, and I get free packs of unreleased seeds. Winner winner chicken dinner.Dun Dun Dunnnnnnnnn!!!!Everything was going so well until about week 4. I found about 5 fully open male flowers on Wx#4 on a way low down branch hidden away very well. I removed them immediately, sprayed everything down with water to kill any remaining pollen and searched all plants for any further male flowers and couldnêt find anything. I knew from the second I found them that there was going to be seeds in this crop. Its a real shame, but I was already half way into flowering so it didnêt make sense to start over. I figured Iêd have to ride it out and see what happens. Worse case scenario, the whole crop gets turned into Live Rosin.I cant really fault the genetics themselves. Its possible that I had a light leak as this plant was closest to an external light source, but Iêve never had this issue before and never actually saw the light leak but its definitely possible that it was my fault in some way, and not the genetics.Well here we are. I refer to Wx#4 as Ground 0 from here on out. It and the 2 adjacent plants had some heavily seeded buds at harvest. Those buds went straight into the freezer to be made into Live Rosin. Those plants were seeded the worse, but no plants escaped unscathed. Even the SSH x •88G13HP which was on the opposite side of the room has some seeds.In case you didnêt know, seeds make no difference to vapers. Since they arenêt being combusted they donêt give off anything bad that we donêt want. If they make it into the pave it just takes up a little room in the pave but doesnêt influence the flavor or effect in anyway. Smokers on the other hand need to be more careful. Smoking seeds doesnêt taste very nice and is reported to possibly give headaches.These seeds are very mature(large) and easy to see in the grinder, but it is possible to grind them up and make it a pain to pick out. Usually if you pick a bud apart well when putting it into the grinder you will see/feel the seeds and can remove them easily. They are easy to find if you know to look for the hard, extra swollen calyxes.Now Iêve always said that I wish people wouldnêt smoke my weed. I put far too much time effort, energy, and soul, to just have it all go up in smoke. Not to mention that vaping is way more efficient, healthier and an overall completely better experience. I blow smokers mind with my Mighty all the time(I donêt think its just my weed anyways haha). Vaping is much more pleasurable experience. If you have the means to afford my weed you should have the means to afford a nice vape. I recommend anything from Stork and Bickel(German engineering at its finest for our needs). The vaping experience is next level and doesnêt compare. Evolve with us from the cavemen that we were, leave the fire behind, and embrace the technology of the 21st century to improve your life. Think of it as an investment in your health and financially as it WILL stretch your herb out and make it last longer.Anyways, all I can say is this:If you are going to buy/smoke weed from this crop expect it to have some seeds in it. All I can do is be completely honest, and discount it to make it worth your while. The flavour and effects of these plants are fully intact, and there is definitely some magic in there, no doubt about that. Vapers Rejoice.-Canna

listing: 1000ml Blazing Vapor THC Cannabis Vape eJuice
description: Blazing Vapor is a potent THC eJuice blend containing Purple OG Kush and Phantom Cookies and can be vaped as is for a super strong and intense high, or diluted with Vegetable Glycol (VG) and/or Propylene Glycol (PG) to make your oil last longer.FLAVORMany of you have told us you prefer the natural taste of pot so we havenêt added any flavors but feel free to add your own. Adding flavor masks that give away smell of pot and allows you to vape undetected in public. Now thatês a bonus!INFUSED NOT EXTRACTEDBlazing Vapor is infused with a 67% VG to 33% PG ratio. No butane or propane (lighter fuel), ethanol (alcohol) or isopropyl (rubbing alcohol) has been used in the cannabis extraction process.CONCENTRATEWhen used undiluted it can clog your vaporizerês coil faster than a nicotine infusion. While both PG and VG will work to extend the life of your coil, PG is thinner and will keep your coil unclogged the longest.For those unfamiliar with VG and PG, these two products are found in just about all eliquids and in the case of Blazing Vapor work to suspend cannabis trichomes until heat is applied which converts THC to its psychedelic form which is what gets you high. VG produces the billowing clouds of vapor often associated with vaping and has a sweeter taste, while PG produced much less smoke and has a throat hit that is often preferred by smokers. Many users prefer to dilute with a combination of both PG and VG.VAPORIZER SETTINGSWe recommend you set your vaporizer to around 50W for the optimal vaping experience. If youêre not feeling an effect experiment with different temperature settings.STEALTHWe use various methods to avoid detection and your Blazing Vapor will be unlabeled. The images are for illustrative purpose.ORDERING ESCROWKindly finalize your order to release the funds when they are held in escrow.

listing: 20ml ** GELATO ** Vape THC Eliquid
description: ROSIN ON PROMOTION WITH THE BEST PRICESWe want present you –Green Connection Extractions”.Rosin make with press. Very clean without solventless Shatter Rosin.Make with a GELATO grown on hydroponics systems, amazing flavour.What Is Rosin?Items needed to make rosin include dried cannabis flower, a hair straightening iron, a metal tool, and wax paper Rosin refers to an extraction process that utilizes a combination of heat and pressure to nearly instantaneously squeeze resinous sap from your initial staçrting material. The term –rosin” originated as a method of making a product used to create friction with violin bows. With cannabis, this method is incredibly versatile in that it can either be used with flowers or to clean up hash and kief into a full-melt hash oil. The result is a translucent, sappy, and sometimes shatter-like product. If executed correctly, rosin can rival the flavor, potency, and yield of other solvent-based extraction products.Why Is Rosin So Popular? Macro photo of cannabis rosin extract on a dab tool One reason for rosinês newfound popularity is that itês a solventless technique, meaning the process does not require use of any foreign substances. Instead, rosin uses a mechanical process involving heat and pressure to extract the resin from the plant. Other extraction methods utilize light hydrocarbons such as butane and/or propane. Often, these complex and mechanical systems require a lengthy purge to safely remove most, if not all of the residual solvents from the final product.Rosin, on the other hand, simply uses heat and pressure and does not require any additional cleaning, so your final product is clean and ready in just minutes. When compared to BHO (butane hash oil), the two are aesthetically indistinguishable. Rosin, when made properly, retains just as many valuable terpenes that account for aroma and flavor. However, in a lab test, rosin will never contain a single parts per million (PPM) of residual hydrocarbon. In other words, you are essentially getting shatter without any solvents when using this process.

listing: Bodhi's - Orgasmatron x('88G13xHashplant) Unreleased Cross!
description: As always:Grown by meIndoor with renewable energy. Indoor quality with an outdoor carbon footprint.Organically grown in soil for extra terpene expression and quality.Hand manicured while –wet” to keep as many crystals on the bud as possible.Cured to perfection!This should be priced like my tier 1, but Iêm going to price this as tier 2 which is 10% cheaper due to the LIGHTLY SEEDED status. Also having a 20% sale on this so please take advantage of it while it lasts!!LIGHTLY SEEDED TLDR;(too long didnêt read): This new crop has some seeds unfortunately. Iêve removed the heavily seeded buds to be used for Live Rosin, and removed all the seeds that I saw when trimming, but there are still a small amount of seeds you may come across. This doesnêt matter much to vapers, but for you dirty smoking combusters out thereÄ Youêve been warned. They are easy enough to avoid in the grinder. This is still fantastic herb, but I have to be upfront and honest and warn you. Iêve sent out some samples to some of my regular customers and no one seemed to mind an occasional seed here or there.You might even want to keep what you find incase you want to try and grow some in the future. Alternatively throw them into government gardens as a form of protest.If you are still interested please read on.PEDIGREEOrgasmatron x •88 G13 x Hashplant('88G13HP AKA MR. Nice)Orgasmatron and Wookie are known as Bodhiês best concentrate strains. They are smell and flavour sensations to say the least.Orgasmatron = Nepali OG x Stevie Wonder (Sensi Star x Train Wreck x Blueberry x Bubba Kush)https://en.seedfinder.eu/strain-info/Nepali_OG/Unknown_or_Legendary/ https://en.seedfinder.eu/strain-info/Stevie_Wonder/Bodhi_Seeds/ https://en.seedfinder.eu/strain-info/88_G-13_HashPlant/Unknown_or_Legendary/These sisters all look the same with very similar indica leaning relaxing effects. They are terp explosions with high levels of tons of so many different terpenes. You will get lots of Citrus, Berry, Floral, Pine, and Spice.They all smell and taste just a bit different to a trained pallete. Feel free to tell me with your address if you would like a specific one, or if you ask nicely Iêll let you pick 2. Otherwise Iêll pick 1 for you.O1: Smells: Juniper berries, connifer berries. Fruity and piney. Tastes: Lemon meringue pie, Berry cheese cake , hints of pine.02: Smells: Florally, anise, black pepper Taste: Floral, lemon , berry.06: Slightly spongier buds than the others of this cross. Smells: Fruit punch, florally mixed berry sweets. Touch of malt and anise. Taste: Spicey wasabi, lemon, berry, floral, black pepper.O10: Smell: Caramel, syrup, cream, citrus, touch of florally fushia. Taste: Florally, Citrus, Spice, Lemon, LimeSorry it took me an extra 2 months to get these listed, but on the bright side the herb got an extra 2 month cure. Thats always a good thing :DReason for the delay is Iêve been crazy busy with my total grow room rehaul and upgrades. Iêve taken 2 giant leaps. 1 from HPS grow lights to cutting edge state of the art leds. Iêve also moved from bottled organics to notill organic living soil. I only use plain water now and organic dry amendments are added to the soil that even has worms living in it. The whole focus now is on the soil food web. Prepare for some extreme terpene expressions on my future crops.If you like this, your going to love the Live Rosin Iêm making from this as well.If you followed me on CGMC you probably saw me announce this exciting seed test that I just finished.The seed test was for 2 currently unreleased crosses from Bodhi Seeds. Bodhi is one of the most sought after Breeders on the Planet. All while being family owned and operated. Bodhi himself, produces unique, high-quality cannabis crosses. Utilizing organic and sustainable practices, Bodhi creates some of the highest quality genetics and effective flowers available today. Hes done some podcasts, check him out if thats something you are into. I suggest the 2 parter on The POTCAST with Heavy Daze.I have a big place in my heart for Bodhi. The work he does, him as a lovely person in general, and his attitude towards breeding checks all the boxes for me. As soon as I heard him say that he loves to help plants have sex, I knew I found some one that vibes with me. That and all of his practices jive with my own.If youêve had the opportunity to try either Black Raspberry(currently sold out, OMG its so magic, and just so happens to be half Wookie) or Sunshine Daydream, youêll have a good idea on what some of his genetics can do.I was lucky enough to use an old contact on the west coast to request an opportunity to seed test for the man himself. I was graciously received 1 pack each of:Wookie 7(Black Raspberryês uncle) x Space Monkey (Gorilla Glue 4 x Wookie #15) https://en.seedfinder.eu/strain-info/Space_Monkey/Bodhi_Seeds/Orgasmatron x •88G13HP https://en.seedfinder.eu/strain-info/Wookie_Orgasm/Bodhi_Seeds/The cool thing about a seed test is that weêre both doing each other a favour. Iêm helping him test unreleased seeds to make sure there are no problems and give him a detailed report back, and I get free packs of unreleased seeds. Winner winner chicken dinner.Dun Dun Dunnnnnnnnn!!!!Everything was going so well until about week 4. I found about 5 fully open male flowers on Wx#4 on a way low down branch hidden away very well. I removed them immediately, sprayed everything down with water to kill any remaining pollen and searched all plants for any further male flowers and couldnêt find anything. I knew from the second I found them that there was going to be seeds in this crop. Its a real shame, but I was already half way into flowering so it didnêt make sense to start over. I figured Iêd have to ride it out and see what happens. Worse case scenario, the whole crop gets turned into Live Rosin.I cant really fault the genetics themselves. Its possible that I had a light leak as this plant was closest to an external light source, but Iêve never had this issue before and never actually saw the light leak but its definitely possible that it was my fault in some way, and not the genetics.Well here we are. I refer to Wx#4 as Ground 0 from here on out. It and the 2 adjacent plants had some heavily seeded buds at harvest. Those buds went straight into the freezer to be made into Live Rosin. Those plants were seeded the worse, but no plants escaped unscathed. Even the SSH x •88G13HP which was on the opposite side of the room has some seeds.In case you didnêt know, seeds make no difference to vapers. Since they arenêt being combusted they donêt give off anything bad that we donêt want. If they make it into the pave it just takes up a little room in the pave but doesnêt influence the flavor or effect in anyway. Smokers on the other hand need to be more careful. Smoking seeds doesnêt taste very nice and is reported to possibly give headaches.These seeds are very mature(large) and easy to see in the grinder, but it is possible to grind them up and make it a pain to pick out. Usually if you pick a bud apart well when putting it into the grinder you will see/feel the seeds and can remove them easily. They are easy to find if you know to look for the hard, extra swollen calyxes.Now Iêve always said that I wish people wouldnêt smoke my weed. I put far too much time effort, energy, and soul, to just have it all go up in smoke. Not to mention that vaping is way more efficient, healthier and an overall completely better experience. I blow smokers mind with my Mighty all the time(I donêt think its just my weed anyways haha). Vaping is much more pleasurable experience. If you have the means to afford my weed you should have the means to afford a nice vape. I recommend anything from Stork and Bickel(German engineering at its finest for our needs). The vaping experience is next level and doesnêt compare. Evolve with us from the cavemen that we were, leave the fire behind, and embrace the technology of the 21st century to improve your life. Think of it as an investment in your health and financially as it WILL stretch your herb out and make it last longer.Anyways, all I can say is this:If you are going to buy/smoke weed from this crop expect it to have some seeds in it. All I can do is be completely honest, and discount it to make it worth your while. The flavour and effects of these plants are fully intact, and there is definitely some magic in there, no doubt about that. Vapers Rejoice.-Canna

listing: 5ml ** GELATO ** Vape THC Eliquid
description: ROSIN ON PROMOTION WITH THE BEST PRICESWe want present you –Green Connection Extractions”.Rosin make with press. Very clean without solventless Shatter Rosin.Make with a GELATO grown on hydroponics systems, amazing flavour.What Is Rosin?Items needed to make rosin include dried cannabis flower, a hair straightening iron, a metal tool, and wax paper Rosin refers to an extraction process that utilizes a combination of heat and pressure to nearly instantaneously squeeze resinous sap from your initial staçrting material. The term –rosin” originated as a method of making a product used to create friction with violin bows. With cannabis, this method is incredibly versatile in that it can either be used with flowers or to clean up hash and kief into a full-melt hash oil. The result is a translucent, sappy, and sometimes shatter-like product. If executed correctly, rosin can rival the flavor, potency, and yield of other solvent-based extraction products.Why Is Rosin So Popular? Macro photo of cannabis rosin extract on a dab tool One reason for rosinês newfound popularity is that itês a solventless technique, meaning the process does not require use of any foreign substances. Instead, rosin uses a mechanical process involving heat and pressure to extract the resin from the plant. Other extraction methods utilize light hydrocarbons such as butane and/or propane. Often, these complex and mechanical systems require a lengthy purge to safely remove most, if not all of the residual solvents from the final product.Rosin, on the other hand, simply uses heat and pressure and does not require any additional cleaning, so your final product is clean and ready in just minutes. When compared to BHO (butane hash oil), the two are aesthetically indistinguishable. Rosin, when made properly, retains just as many valuable terpenes that account for aroma and flavor. However, in a lab test, rosin will never contain a single parts per million (PPM) of residual hydrocarbon. In other words, you are essentially getting shatter without any solvents when using this process.

listing: 10ml ** GELATO ** Vape THC Eliquid
description: ROSIN ON PROMOTION WITH THE BEST PRICESWe want present you –Green Connection Extractions”.Rosin make with press. Very clean without solventless Shatter Rosin.Make with a GELATO grown on hydroponics systems, amazing flavour.What Is Rosin?Items needed to make rosin include dried cannabis flower, a hair straightening iron, a metal tool, and wax paper Rosin refers to an extraction process that utilizes a combination of heat and pressure to nearly instantaneously squeeze resinous sap from your initial staçrting material. The term –rosin” originated as a method of making a product used to create friction with violin bows. With cannabis, this method is incredibly versatile in that it can either be used with flowers or to clean up hash and kief into a full-melt hash oil. The result is a translucent, sappy, and sometimes shatter-like product. If executed correctly, rosin can rival the flavor, potency, and yield of other solvent-based extraction products.Why Is Rosin So Popular? Macro photo of cannabis rosin extract on a dab tool One reason for rosinês newfound popularity is that itês a solventless technique, meaning the process does not require use of any foreign substances. Instead, rosin uses a mechanical process involving heat and pressure to extract the resin from the plant. Other extraction methods utilize light hydrocarbons such as butane and/or propane. Often, these complex and mechanical systems require a lengthy purge to safely remove most, if not all of the residual solvents from the final product.Rosin, on the other hand, simply uses heat and pressure and does not require any additional cleaning, so your final product is clean and ready in just minutes. When compared to BHO (butane hash oil), the two are aesthetically indistinguishable. Rosin, when made properly, retains just as many valuable terpenes that account for aroma and flavor. However, in a lab test, rosin will never contain a single parts per million (PPM) of residual hydrocarbon. In other words, you are essentially getting shatter without any solvents when using this process.

listing: Amnesia Haze New Vendor Good Grade
description: Not grown by me, it is better than your average street herbs, not close to passing classed as high quality, but good. The grower is much better at trimming than me - personally I prefer better quality ;)It does what it is meant to do. It has a fast acting sativa effect, not potent, with a much milder indica hit if any at all. You could probably smoke/vape this all day.MMAmnesia Haze has a somewhat misleading name: itês a sativa-dominant hybrid that, despite its potency, wonêt leave you with a severely impaired memory. Composed from a cross of staple strain Haze and several different worldwide landraces, including Thai, Hawaiian, and Afghani, Amnesia Haze may actually drive inspiration rather than forgetfulness. The Afghani indica in its genetics makes for a well-balanced, albeit somewhat cerebral high.Cannabis cup winning genetics.

listing: 250ml Blazing Vapor THC Cannabis Vape eJuice
description: Blazing Vapor is a potent THC eJuice blend containing Purple OG Kush and Phantom Cookies and can be vaped as is for a super strong and intense high, or diluted with Vegetable Glycol (VG) and/or Propylene Glycol (PG) to make your oil last longer.FLAVORMany of you have told us you prefer the natural taste of pot so we havenêt added any flavors but feel free to add your own. Adding flavor masks that give away smell of pot and allows you to vape undetected in public. Now thatês a bonus!INFUSED NOT EXTRACTEDBlazing Vapor is infused with a 67% VG to 33% PG ratio. No butane or propane (lighter fuel), ethanol (alcohol) or isopropyl (rubbing alcohol) has been used in the cannabis extraction process.CONCENTRATEWhen used undiluted it can clog your vaporizerês coil faster than a nicotine infusion. While both PG and VG will work to extend the life of your coil, PG is thinner and will keep your coil unclogged the longest.For those unfamiliar with VG and PG, these two products are found in just about all eliquids and in the case of Blazing Vapor work to suspend cannabis trichomes until heat is applied which converts THC to its psychedelic form which is what gets you high. VG produces the billowing clouds of vapor often associated with vaping and has a sweeter taste, while PG produced much less smoke and has a throat hit that is often preferred by smokers. Many users prefer to dilute with a combination of both PG and VG.VAPORIZER SETTINGSWe recommend you set your vaporizer to around 50W for the optimal vaping experience. If youêre not feeling an effect experiment with different temperature settings.STEALTHWe use various methods to avoid detection and your Blazing Vapor will be unlabeled. The images are for illustrative purpose.ORDERING ESCROWKindly finalize your order to release the funds when they are held in escrow.

listing: Triple Strength THC CannaJuice For Ecigs All New Formula!!
description: 3ml minimum order. Bottles available are 3, 5, 10, 30mlThis is very EXciting to offer a new juice! We have spent years making e-juice and finally have got a perfect process down. This EXtreme E-juice is the first CannaJuice we have made with this new process and formula that contains only the finest ingredients. The contents of the new EXtreme E-juice are PEG400, BHO, & d-Limeonene for flavor enhancement. This process leaves and very smooth tasting and EXtremely potent version of the E-cigarette CannaJuice we all long for. This will work in virtually any of the E-cigs on the market today. The juice is easily poured out of the small bottle it arrives packaged in, into almost any cartridge or tank on virtually any e-cig on the market. All ingredients are food quality and the EXtreme E-juice is made with love so it is even edible if desired (though not recommended by us). Each bottle contains high quality double vacuum purged BHO. The BHO is extracted using cryogenic extraction methods in an award winning, closed loop BHOgart extractor using N-butane to leave behind nasty plant matter and waxes. The BHO is then put in a vacuum oven at low temps to savior the terpenes and extremely great tastes twice. We have spent countless hours trying to perfect this juice and this is as close as perfection gets when it comes to CannaJuice. If you want that EXtreme E-juice that will set you straight with just a few tokes, then this juice is for you. We have left .gov links below to explain what d-Limeonene and PEG400 are to calm any qualms about them.d-Limonene link {Clearnet Warning}http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/18072821PEG400 link {Clearnet Warning}http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC185333/

listing: 9ml DMT E-liquid
description: Made ready to use with any sub ohm tank, each 3ml tinted vial contains 1g NN DMT. DMT used is the same listed on the store and PG/VG is from a trusted source, not from China. This mix does not contain any flavoring.The freebase used in this mix is the same as listed –NN DMT”.Custom orders made with the –High Purity NN DMT” can be made on request.User Guidelines    Fill tank up with liquid, avoid dilution (smaller hits can be taken if the experience is too intense)    Recommended setting is 50W but have had good results within 40W-80W    Breath in for 3 seconds and hold for 10 seconds (if 3 seconds is too long to draw take multiple 1-2 second breaths and hold in for 10 seconds)    Repeat until launch, keeping in mind the last repetition could be a challengeSomething to keep note of is that the effects stack within a time frame. If you have difficulties holding in the vapor try taking smaller hits, remembering to hold in the vapor for as long as possible. You can repeat these small tokes over the next 90 seconds but try to get where you want to be within a minute.Intended price before market fees = $270.30 AUD.
